Package: pdftextclusteR
Title: Detecting Text Clusters in PDF Documents Using Density-Based Clustering Algorithms
Version: 0.0.0.9008
Authors@R: 
    person("Coen", "Eisma", , "coeneisma@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-9001-2572"))
Description: Detect and extract text clusters, such as columns and text boxes, 
    from PDF documents. Utilizes the 'pdftools' package for PDF import and 
    applies density-based clustering algorithms from the 'dbscan' package to 
    accurately group related text elements, facilitating improved text analysis 
    and extraction from complex PDF layouts.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://coeneisma.github.io/pdftextclusteR/, https://github.com/coeneisma/pdftextclusteR
